articles.title: Korg to Debut Minilogue XD at Winter NAMM
articles.summary: KORG’s minilogue has evolved with the release of the minilogue XD. The all-new minilogue XD takes on the form factor of KORG’s best-selling analog synth while adding powerful new features and sound creation possibilities.

articles.title: JOUÉ Introduces the Grand Clavier
articles.summary: New and born of the expressive Magic Modules range, the Grand Clavier has 25 expressive keys to subtly play any type of digital instruments. The Glissando mode allows continuous pitch-bend between notes and to enjoy microtonal interpretation.
